{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"B · Power · saved views + composable filters + group-by + bulk (Linear-ish)\n      Tabs at top for saved views (\"All open\", \"My priorities\", \"This week\", \"Recurring\"). Filter row supports composable predicates (project · status · priority · label · due range · text). Toolbar adds Group-by + Sort. Multi-select with bulk toolbar. URL reflects state.\n      \n        \n        \n          \n            task·mgr\n            ⌕ Search…⌘K\n            \n            🔔☾\n          \n          \n            ▢⌖▥\n            ≡▦🏷⚙\n          \n          \n            \n              All tasks\n              23 open · 47 completed this week\n              + New task\n            \n\n            \n              All open\n              My priorities\n              This week\n              Recurring\n              Inbox (no project)\n              + Save current as view…\n            \n\n            \n              status = open ×\n              ●project ∈ Backend ×\n              priority ≥ medium ×\n              + Add filter…\n            \n\n            \n              Group:Due date\n              Sort:Priority ↓\n              Columns ▾\n              Density ▾\n            \n\n            \n            \n              2 selected\n              ↑↓ to navigate · ⏎ to open · ⌫ delete\n              \n                Complete\n                Set due…\n                Move to project…\n                + Label\n                Delete\n              \n            \n\n            Today 2\n            Write zod-schemas migration doc!medbackendtoday\n            Refactor auth middleware!highbackend2d late\n\n            This week 2\n            Onboard new team lead!highWed\n          \n        \n      \n      Pros: power-user friendly, sharable filtered URLs, bulk operations. Cons: more affordances = more to build (filter operator UI, group-by reactivity, multi-select + keyboard nav). Backend GET /tasks may need extension (currently single-value filters; need OR/IN for ranges and array fields).","choice":"b","id":null,"timestamp":1778871490828}
